abstract: North Korea reports that it has successfully launched new antiship missile.
lead_paragraph: A state media report Saturday quoted Kim Jong-un, the North’s leader, as calling for “more tactical guided weapons of high precision and intelligence.”

headline.main: North Korea Says It Tested New Missile With Success
